content: Net revenue for Apple Inc. for the twelve months ended September 28, 2024, was $391.035 billion, and for the twelve months ended September 30, 2023, it was $383.285 billion. Net revenue is presented as total net sales, including both products and services, in the condensed consolidated statements of operations.
